%% Diagram: Preload scanner racing ahead while the main parser is blocked
%% Type: sequence
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    participant Main as Main Parser
    participant Scan as Preload Scanner
    participant Net as Network

    Main->>Main: Parse <head>
    Main->>Net: Fetch app.js
    Note over Main: Parser blocked on app.js
    Scan->>Scan: Scan ahead through remaining HTML
    Scan->>Net: Fetch styles.css (link rel=stylesheet)
    Scan->>Net: Fetch hero.jpg (img src)
    Scan->>Net: Fetch analytics.js (script src)
    Note over Scan: Scanner only collects URLs<br/>does not build DOM
    Net-->>Main: app.js arrives
    Main->>Main: Execute and resume
    Note over Main: When parser reaches these tags,<br/>resources may already be in cache
